<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="allow-for">allow for</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>考虑到；顾及：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Allowing for the bad weather, we should set off right now. 
考虑到天气不好，我们应该马上出发。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Has everything been allowed for in your plan? 
你的计划是否把各种情况都考虑进去了？</p></div></div>